description:
***TOP 10 (Photo & Video) in 15 iTunes App Store***

PhotoFrame Pro helps you combine multiple photos into amazing looking frames with caption in seconds! 

And share them with your friends and family via Facebook, Email, Instagram, Twitter, Flickr and Tumblr. 

The BEST AND MOST ADVANCED PhotoFrame App in App Store Today. Has ALL THE FEATURES you could want and more. You'll never want to use another frame app after using PhotoFrame! 

***USER REVIEWS***
 
This ones my favorite because of the resizeable feature 

Lots of people like my pics on instagram because of this

I love it, I use it everyday....

I looping this app it is amazing!!!! Best collage app ever!! 

Love playing with different frames and create new photos selections!! 

THIS IS THE BEST PICTURE APP EVER! I wont be surprised if it beats instagram 

***MAIN FEATURES***

- Easy to add word/caption to photo
- Easy to add cute stick(cool emotion icons,love,xmas)
- 60+Well designed photo frames 
- Unique art photo frame collage mode
- 48+ Popular  layouts
- 5 ratios for layout: 1:1, 3:2,2:3,4:3, 2:1
- Apply effects to individual photos
- Add a shadow to the photos
- Easy color picker for the frames background
- Easily move photos to different areas by drag and drop
- Pan, zoom, rotate or mirror images
- Adjust the frame to make it bigger or smaller in real time
- Color the borders
- Make images to rounded corners
- Share via instagram, Facebook, Twitter and Email
